rows.label: qst400305_msg0001
rows.name:
That must be the monster Cedwyn
was talking about.

rows.label: qst400305_msg0002
rows.name:
Doesn't look like a pushover,
that's for sure.

rows.label: qst400305_msg0003
rows.name:
Tora wish could help too, but probably
not much good for anything other than
decoy or lure.

rows.label: qst400305_msg0101
rows.name:
No need for any of that. We can handle
this one just fine! Right, Homura?

rows.label: qst400305_msg0103
rows.name:
No need to rely on just my power,
though. You should make full use
of all your Blades!

rows.label: qst400305_msg0104
rows.name:
Indeed. We may only have one
Driver, but twice the Blades means
twice the potential!
